Program: LR-GLASS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description:

  Endless Analysis.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Content:
  
  makefile	  : MakeFile for build program
  main.C	  : main file

  source	  : Source files
  include	  : Include files
  cards		  : cards files
  example_data	  : data files for example cards
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Syntax: ./lrGlass outputFile.root card.txt dirName plotName 

for help execute: ./lrGlass

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Card Types: 
	-thrEff: Calculate efficiency for threshold scan.
	-volEff: Calculate efficiency for voltage scan.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Support:

  Shchablo@gmail.com
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

System Requirements:

  - ROOT 6.05/02 CERN Library (https://root.cern.ch)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------




